{
  "title": "Floral, Crumbly Kenyan Salmon Kebabs",
  "description": "A dish that balances floral notes with the richness of crumbled Kenyan spices, all infused with the delicacy of salmon. Perfect for meal prep.",
  "cuisine": "Kenyan",
