  "instructions": [
    "Preheat broiler to 400°F (200°C).",
    "In a medium bowl, whisk together Kenyan Spice Blend, Garlic, Ginger, Chili Flakes (if using), and Salt.",
    "Add Coconut Oil, Lemon Juice, and Honey to the bowl. Mix until well combined.",
    "Add chopped Cilantro and Basil to the bowl. Mix until well combined.",
    "Add Coconut Milk to the bowl. Mix until well combined.",
    "Cut salmon fillets into 1-inch (2.5 cm) cubes.",
    "Thread salmon cubes onto skewers, leaving a small space between each piece.",
    "Brush the skewers with the spice mixture, making sure to coat all the salmon pieces.",
    "Place the skewers on a baking sheet lined with parchment paper.",
    "Broil for 8-10 minutes, flipping halfway through, or until cooked through.",
    "Serve hot with additional Cilantro and Basil for garnish."
  ],
